verseObjects.content: + \ft Some ancient copies have, \fqa two men are looking for you \fqa* or \fqa some men are looking for you \fqa*.
+ \ft Some ancient copies add: \fqa When he comes, he will speak to you \fqa* .
+ \ft Instead of \fqa instructed by the Lord to say, \fqa* some ancient copies have, \fqa instructed by God to say \fqa* .
